= SDL_IsScreenSaverEnabled =
Use this function to return whether the screensaver is currently enabled (default off).


== Syntax ==
```c++
SDL_bool SDL_IsScreenSaverEnabled(void)
```

== Return Value ==
Returns true if the screen saver is enabled, false if it is disabled.  

